{"word":"μέλισσα","slug":"μέλισσα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μέλισσα</b></el> <el>(μέλισσᾰ, <el>attic</el> <el>-ττα, ης, ἡ</el>,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μέλι'><el>μέλι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a bee</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>apis</el>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>one of the priestesses</i> of Delphi, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <a href='S:μέλι'><el>μέλι</el></a>, <i>honey</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}